INSERT INTO `SiteTree` VALUES (86,'HomePage','2007-10-01 12:47:24','2025-06-26 02:14:19','home','Welcome to the public demo of the Silverstripe CMS','Home','<div id=\"Thanks\">\n<p class=\"intro\" style=\"text-align: left;\">The Silverstripe CMS is an open source web content management system used by governments, businesses, and non-profit organisations around the world. It is a powerful tool for professional web development teams, and web content authors rave about how easy it is to use.</p>\n<p class=\"intro\" style=\"text-align: left;\">[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/cms-page-edit-large.png\" id=\"47484\" width=\"600\" height=\"474\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>\n<h3>Silverstripe CMS</h3>\n<p>As a platform, the Silverstripe CMS is used to build websites, intranets and web applications. The modern architecture of the Silverstripe CMS allows organisations to keep pace with innovation on the web. The Silverstripe CMS enables websites and applications to contain stunning design, great content as well as compelling interactive and social functions.</p>\n<h3>Silverstripe Framework</h3>\n<p>Besides a powerful and intuitive content authoring application, the Silverstripe CMS contains a powerful PHP based programming framework. The Silverstripe Framework brings immense flexibility and ease in customising your site and provides fundamentals such as security models, workflow, caching and multiple language support.</p>\n</div>','Welcome to the Silverstripe CMS Open Source CMS demo','this is my test of this website template...','silverstripe 3, demo, cms, html5, open source content management system, php',1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,0,'Published',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,0,295,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers','en_US',0,0,0),(102,'Page','2007-10-01 12:47:24','2025-06-23 23:42:32','about','About',NULL,'<p class=\"intro\">This demo is to show off the authoring interface of the Silverstripe Content Management System (CMS). The Silverstripe CMS is designed to be super easy to update content, allowing designers and developers to build rich, amazing websites.</p>\n<p>To try out Silverstripe CMS for yourself youll need to log in as an web administrator which will allow you to make changes to the content of this demo website.</p>\n<h3>Startup theme</h3>\n<p>This demo uses the Startup theme which is the default theme provided in the standard download of the Silverstripe CMS with some additional modifications for the purpose of this demo. Simple theme is easy to use and understand. We have kept it basic so those with minimal understanding of CSS and HTML can adapt it to suit their needs. The Startup&nbsp;theme is also used in Silverstripe CMS theme tutorials, giving you simple tips to get you started on your own theme creation.</p>\n<h3>Friendly and flexible open source CMS</h3>\n<p>The Silverstripe CMS is designed to promote accessible site design, semantic markup, and HTML5 use. With its template flexibility, we\'re confident that it will be able to accommodate whatever is coming next. It has been downloaded well over 500,000 times and powers websites for government agencies, corporations, non-profits and a large number of much smaller websites.</p>\n<p>We believe the open source model simply produces better web software and in turn, better meets our own needs and those of other developers who use the software. As with all open source software, anyone has access to the source code, and a global community of developers can share best practices, code, documentation, roadmap ideas and so on.</p>\n<p>You never have to pay a licensing fee for Silverstripe CMS, and you never have to worry about vendor lock-in. Under the BSD license, which is one of the most flexible open source licenses and Open Source Initiative approved, you benefit from the contributions of others in the community, and the transparent way in which the software is developed in consultation with its users.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,2,NULL,0,0,'Published',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',1,1,0,94,1,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers','en_US',0,0,0),(202,'Page','2007-10-01 12:47:24','2025-06-26 01:13:20','contact','Contact',NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you are a developer wanting to know more about Silverstripe, check out <a title=\"Help and Support\" href=\"https://www.silverstripe.org/help-and-support/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Help and Support</a> for&nbsp;a list of resources and documentation&nbsp;for the Silverstripe CMS open source CMS and the Silverstripe Framework.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Social Media</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Follow Silverstripe on <a title=\"Silverstripe Twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/silverstripe\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> or <a title=\"Silverstripe Facebook\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silverstripe\">Facebook</a> for the latest updates and community news. Check out Silverstripe\'s <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/silverstripe\">Vimeo account</a>&nbsp;for any official videos.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Silvertripe Ltd.</h3>\n<p>Want to know more about the company that brought you Silverstripe CMS? Then check out <a title=\"Silverstripe Ltd\" href=\"https://silverstripe.com\">silverstripe.com</a></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,6,NULL,0,0,'Published',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',1,1,0,92,1,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers','en_US',0,0,0),(502,'SilverStripe\\ErrorPage\\ErrorPage','2007-10-01 12:47:25','2012-08-29 10:03:38','page-not-found','Page not found',NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Sorry, it seems you were trying to access a page that doesn\'t exist.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Please check the spelling of the URL you were trying to access and try again.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,0,7,NULL,0,0,'Published',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',1,1,0,15,1,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers','en_US',0,0,0),(6670,'SilverStripe\\ErrorPage\\ErrorPage','2010-08-19 12:31:00','2012-05-21 19:34:28','server-error','Server error',NULL,'<p>Sorry, there was a problem with handling your request.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,0,8,NULL,0,0,'New page',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit','en_US',0,0,0),(6672,'Page','2012-05-24 17:32:21','2025-06-24 00:37:39','media-insertion','Media insertion',NULL,'<p>You can insert media from a variety of sites into your page, thanks to the magic of oEmbed! Just click the \"insert media\" button (it looks like a picture of a tree) and enter the URL of your video (YouTube, Vimeo), photo (Flickr, or URL).</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/media-from-web.png\" id=\"47491\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>','Media insertion',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,23,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(6674,'Page','2012-05-25 08:28:48','2025-06-25 05:19:19','responsive','Responsive',NULL,'<p class=\"intro\">The Startup theme has been built using responsive styling. This means when you reduce the width of your browser window, the site will adapt to the screen size.</p>\n<div class=\"captionImage leftAlone\" style=\"width: 600px;\">[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/responsive.png\" id=\"47482\" width=\"600\" height=\"326\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]\n<p class=\"caption leftAlone\">Ministry of Science Innovation working responsively on difference devices</p>\n</div>\n<p>Responsive web design is an approach aimed at crafting sites to provide an optimal viewing experience - easy reading and navigation with minimal resizing, panning, and scrolling - across a wide range of devices (from mobile phones to desktop computer monitors).</p>\n<p>This behaviour is provided by the default with the theme. Alternatively, you can also view this page on your favourite smartphone to see how the theme adjusts to a specific device. The menus and other elements of the page will change to be mobile or tablet friendly.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/0f0943bb26/theme-responsive.png\" id=\"47493\" width=\"600\" height=\"500\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>','Responsive',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6678,40,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(6676,'Page','2012-05-25 10:09:09','2025-06-24 00:37:11','easy-page-editing','Easy page editing',NULL,'<p class=\"intro\">It\'s easy to locate a page to edit, and the rich-text editor makes content updating very simple. Adding pages, links, images and videos can all be done from your web browser without technical or HTML knowledge.</p>\n<h3>Beautiful interface</h3>\n<p>Content authors will just love that they can do their work more quickly, using a beautiful user interface.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A site can have any number of page <em>types</em>, each with their own editable fields, templates and behaviour. A developer can invent new types of fields and behaviour both in the CMS and for the public-facing website. This enables both the CMS and the website to be perfectly tailored to suit requirements.</p>\n<p>The notion of a Draft and Published site enables you to save and preview your changes before the public see it.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/cms-page-edit-large.png\" id=\"47484\" width=\"600\" height=\"474\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>','New Features',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,28,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(6678,'Page','2012-05-25 10:58:19','2025-06-24 00:39:01','theme','Simple Theme','Theme','<p class=\"intro\">Startup theme is the default theme which comes bundled with a new installation of Silverstripe. If you download Silverstripe CMS without this theme you can also find it on <a title=\"Startup theme download\" href=\"https://github.com/silverstripe/startup-theme/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">github.com</a> to use and alter as you wish.</p>\n<p>Themes can be tailored to the needs of a business or individual through basic HTML and CSS which every web developer is familiar with. Within a theme developers have the opportunity to build custom features like forms, image carousels and news pages using Silverstripe CMS and Framework speed up the development process.</p>\n<p>Themes usually consist of built-in typographical styles so that content authors can choose from a predefined set font choices with set colours and size. Removing the option for content authors to chose font colours and faces produces better professionalism of the website, and makes the editing interface simpler. It also means you can later change the visual appearance or theme of your website without altering your written content.</p>','Styles',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,5,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,0,26,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(6681,'Page','2012-05-25 13:52:37','2025-06-24 00:18:06','security-and-audit-trail','Security & Audit Trail',NULL,'<p>Every save made to a page contributes to an audit trail. You can compare old versions with each other and roll back to them in the History tab.</p>\n<p>A powerful security system allows viewing and editing of pages to be restricted to various users. Users and groups can be created and this can all provide the basis for secure login areas or more elaborate publishing workflow.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/page-settings.png\" id=\"47489\" width=\"600\" height=\"475\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>','Security & Audit Trail',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,9,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,14,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','OnlyTheseUsers',NULL,0,0,0),(6686,'Page','2012-06-29 08:46:36','2025-06-25 05:21:42','features','Silverstripe CMS & Framework features','Features','<p class=\"intro\"><span>The Silverstripe CMS is easy for both developers and content authors to work with. The Silverstripe </span>Framework<span>&nbsp;keeps the code tucked away neatly so that it can be accessed easily by programmers without getting in the way of content authors.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span>An out-of-the-box installation of the Silverstripe CMS provides all the day-to-day editing control you are likely to need as a content author. With WYSIWYG and drag &amp; drop functions, site editors have full control over the way they want their content to look without needing to know HTML. If you can use a word processor, you can use the Silverstripe CMS. Images and files can be added through a drag &amp; drop interface, and pages and templates are fully customisable. Themes and widgets allow even more extensions. Developers can further customise the interface to suit how you work as an author and as a business.</span></p>\n<p><a title=\"Silverstripe CMS Features\" href=\"https://silverstripe.org/features\">For a complete list of features please visit silverstripe.org</a></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,0,26,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(7197,'Page','2013-10-04 13:37:19','2025-06-25 05:20:27','silverstripe-cms','Silverstripe CMS',NULL,'<div class=\"captionImage leftAlone\" style=\"width: 600px;\">[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/cms-page-edit-small.png\" id=\"47483\" width=\"600\" height=\"468\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]\n<p class=\"caption leftAlone\">Silverstripe CMS interface</p>\n</div>\n<h3>Friendly and flexible open source CMS</h3>\n<p>The Silverstripe CMS is designed to promote accessible site design and semantic markup. With its template flexibility, we\'re confident that it will be able to accommodate whatever is coming next. It has been downloaded well over 500,000 times and powers websites for government agencies, corporations, non-profits and a large number of much smaller websites.</p>\n<p>We believe the open source model simply produces better web software and in turn, better meets our own needs and those of other developers who use the software. As with all open source software, anyone has access to the source code, and a global community of developers can share best practices, code, documentation, roadmap ideas and so on.</p>\n<p>You never have to pay a licensing fee for Silverstripe CMS, and you never have to worry about vendor lock-in. Under the BSD license, which is one of the most flexible open source licenses and Open Source Initiative approved, you benefit from the contributions of others in the community, and the transparent way in which the software is developed in consultation with its users.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,19,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(7198,'Page','2013-10-04 13:59:38','2025-06-25 05:20:47','silverstripe-framework','Silverstripe Framework',NULL,'<p><span class=\"intro\">Besides a powerful and intuitive content authoring application, the Silverstripe CMS contains a powerful PHP based framework. The Silverstripe Framework brings immense flexibility and ease in customising your site and provides fundamentals such as security models, workflow, caching as well as multiple language and sub-site support.</span></p>\n<h3>Under the hood</h3>\n<p>Behind the clean CMS and website presentation sits <a href=\"https://www.silverstripe.org/framework-introduction/\">Silverstripe Framework</a>. Website developers use the framework to write code to create templates, logic and tailor how the CMS works. Developers get the power and flexibility of modern PHP code, while content authors get the simplicity of a tailored CMS.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/code.png\" id=\"47485\" width=\"425\" height=\"360\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,2,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,13,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(7199,'Page','2013-10-04 14:02:04','2025-06-25 05:20:55','silverstripe-community','Silverstripe CMS Community',NULL,'<p class=\"intro\"><a title=\"Visit silverstripe.org\" href=\"https://www.silverstripe.org\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Silverstripe.org</a> is the central hub for the community surrounding the Silverstripe CMS and Framework. The Silverstripe CMS community offers a broad range of support for individuals, companies and organisations as well as for those supporting the future development of the CMS and Framework.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/community.png\" id=\"47486\" width=\"600\" height=\"278\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]<br><a title=\"Silverstripe CMS forums\" href=\"https://forum.silverstripe.org/\">Discussion forums</a><br><a title=\"Community showcase\" href=\"https://www.silverstripe.org/community-showcase/\">Community showcase</a><br><a title=\"Silverstripe CMS Meetups\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/find/?keywords=Silverstripe&amp;radius=Infinity&amp;userFreeform=Wellington%2C+New+Zealand&amp;mcName=Wellington%2C+NZ&amp;lat=-41.300003&amp;lon=174.7833&amp;sort=default\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Silverstripe CMS meetups</a><br><a title=\"Developer directory\" href=\"https://www.silverstripe.org/silverstripe-developer-network/\">Developer directory</a></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,17,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(7200,'Page','2013-10-04 14:14:16','2025-06-24 00:34:35','silverstripe-ltd-','Silverstripe Ltd.',NULL,'<h3>Open source</h3>\n<p>We are strong advocates of open source software. We believe in - and have experienced firsthand - the power of an open developer community. The best way to encourage and create better software is to have people contribute back to the main code base and share their work with others.</p>\n<p>Our flagship product, the Silverstripe Content Management System (CMS), is a free, open source download, alongside Silverstripe Framework, the powerful core which underpins the CMS. The platform is released under the BSD license because we consider it the most business-friendly and developer-friendly license.<br>We have seen strong growth in adoption of our software around the globe. Many of our larger customers are now developing unique and novel solutions on top of Silverstripe CMS and are integrating our software deep into their own product offerings.</p>\n<p>As the technology industry evolves and open source increasingly becomes the default option for businesses, organisations and government, Silverstripe CMS will remain at the centre of this evolution and help push awareness and adoption not only for open source, but related movements such as open data.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,4,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,15,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(7201,'Page','2013-10-08 10:16:22','2025-06-25 05:21:30','support','Silverstripe CMS Support',NULL,'<p><span class=\"intro\">The Silverstripe CMS community are passionate people, making the web a better place through better code, user experiences and engagement.</span></p>\n<p><strong>Silverstripe CMS open source support </strong> <a href=\"https://www.silverstripe.org\">silverstripe.org</a><a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/help-and-support/\"><strong><br></strong></a>If you are looking for help with our open source product, refer to the <a href=\"https://silverstripe.org/help-and-support/\">Help &amp; Support</a> section on our open source community website.<br>You can find:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>documentation for developers</li>\n<li>community resources for developers including forums, realtime conversations, mailing lists</li>\n<li>discussions of core development topics</li>\n<li>the developer directory, helping to source the right developer for the job wherever you are in the world</li>\n<li><span class=\"screen-name\">community events and meetups throughout the world</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>CMS user help</strong>  <a href=\"https://userhelp.silverstripe.org/framework/en/\">userhelp.silverstripe.org</a><br>Resources for website editors, CMS users and administrators.</p>\n<p><strong>Professional support by Silverstripe Ltd.</strong>  <a href=\"https://www.silverstripe.com\">silverstripe.com<br></a>Whatever you need, no matter how big or small, Silverstripe Ltd. can help find a solution that works best for you.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,5,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(7202,'Page','2013-10-08 12:35:21','2025-06-24 00:37:31','file-management','File management',NULL,'<p>With the Silverstripe CMS, users have the capability to upload images and files like PDFs and Word documents to be able to share publicly to the viewer of the site. Uploading an image is easy - just drag the file you want into the insert image window from your desktop. CMS editors also have the option to add files to their content areas from other places on the web.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/file-manager.png\" id=\"47488\" width=\"600\" height=\"456\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,2,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,10,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),(7203,'Page','2013-10-15 11:58:53','2025-06-25 05:22:29','styles-demo','Styles Demo',NULL,'<h2>Typography</h2>\n<p class=\"intro\">Editors have the power to alter the appearance of content within the site using the powerful built-in editor. For example, this introductory text which can be added with the styles that drop down within the CMS editor.</p>\n<div class=\"captionImage leftAlone\" style=\"width: 600px;\">[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/text-style.png\" id=\"47490\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</div>\n<p></p>\n<p>The typography of the Startup theme is designed to create a strong hierarchy with basic styles.</p>\n<h1>Heading &lt;h1&gt;</h1>\n<h2>Heading &lt;h2&gt;</h2>\n<h3>Heading &lt;h3&gt;</h3>\n<h4>Heading &lt;h4&gt;</h4>\n<h5>Heading &lt;h5&gt;</h5>\n<h6>Heading &lt;h6&gt;</h6>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Normal text,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://demo.silverstripe.org/\">hyperlinks</a>,&nbsp;<strong>bold</strong>, and&nbsp;<em>italics</em>.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This is a blockquote style example.&nbsp;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can insert symbols  and Silverstripe CMS supports characters from languages across the globe.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bullet One</li>\n<li>Bullet Two</li>\n<li>Bullet Three</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>List One</li>\n<li>List Two</li>\n<li>List Three</li>\n</ol>\n<h5>Left aligned content</h5>\n<p>Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Nulla vitae elit libero, a pharetra augue. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Maecenas faucibus mollis interdum. Maecenas sed diam eget risus varius blandit sit amet non magna. Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Center aligned content</h5>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Nulla vitae elit libero, a pharetra augue. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Maecenas faucibus mollis interdum. Maecenas sed diam eget risus varius blandit sit amet non magna. Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: right;\">Right aligned content</h5>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Nulla vitae elit libero, a pharetra augue. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Maecenas faucibus mollis interdum. Maecenas sed diam eget risus varius blandit sit amet non magna. Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>\n<div class=\"captionImage leftAlone\