',0,0,102,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(48534,6625,2,0,1,0,'Page','2009-01-26 10:08:20','2009-01-26 10:08:41','in-the-beginning','In The Beginning',NULL,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #4ea3d7; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 1em; line-height: 120%;\">How It All Began</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In 1991, three university friends met up for dinner and got to talking. &nbsp;What if they pooled their knowledge, skills and resources and formed a company, developing a service the like of which the world was crying out for? &nbsp;That night&nbsp;was to witness the initial phases of an amazing metamorphosis, transforming these three regular 9-to-fivers into brilliant, but mad, entrepreneurs...</p>\n<h6 style=\"font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.4em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #666666; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;\">A</span>nd so, after four years, five months, two weeks and three days the metamorphosis was complete and the business formed by their creative genius was released to the world.</h6>\n</span></p>\n</blockquote>','In The Beginning',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,8,NULL,0,0,'Saved (new)',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(48535,6626,1,0,1,0,'Page','2009-01-26 10:15:42','2009-01-26 10:15:42','new-page-3','New Page',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,0,'New page',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6625,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(48536,6626,2,0,1,0,'Page','2009-01-26 10:15:42','2009-01-26 10:20:12','knowledge-and-skills','Knowledge and Skills',NULL,'<p>\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 13.0pt; line-height: 33.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"color: #3298f7; font-family: \'Lucida Grande\';\">\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 13.0pt; line-height: 33.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #3298f7;\">Brian Calhoun</span></p>\n<p  style=\"text-align: right; line-height: 21.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-family: Georgia; color: #333333;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 22.0pt; line-height: 17.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #666666;\">CEO</span></p>\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 24.0pt; line-height: 20.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-family: Georgia; color: #333333;\">Brian brings over 19 years of software and web industry experience mostly in Silicon Valley and since 2004, Brian\'s been a proud Wellingtonian</span></p>\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 24.0pt; line-height: 20.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-family: Georgia; color: #333333;\">Since his appointment as CEO in 2007, Brian has led the company by providing vision and experience to a wide range of efforts: core technology direction, technical and process infrastructure, product offerings, and <a href=\"http://silverstripe.com/agile-approach/\"><span style=\"color: #41a3f8; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Agile project management</span></a> that all combine to make Silverstripe CMS hum. In addition, he\'s the go-to guy for all things grey-hair-corporate-related.</span></p>\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 24.0pt; line-height: 20.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-family: Georgia; color: #333333;\">Brian has contributed to and implemented open source CMS products here in New Zealand and in the U.S. He has led web projects and architected sites for over 12 years, including government and commercial sites in New Zealand.</span></p>\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 24.0pt; line-height: 20.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-family: Georgia; color: #333333;\">Silverstripe is excited to have Brian on board, helping to ensure Silverstripe stays true to the original vision while providing new vision and leadership as well.</span></p>\n<p  style=\"margin-bottom: 22.0pt; line-height: 17.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #666666;\">Check out Brian Calhoun\'s profile <a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/ForumMemberProfile/show/12\"><span style=\"color: #41a3f8; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">here</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #666666;\">Interested in joining the team?Then check out <a href=\"http://silverstripe.com/careers/\"><span style=\"color: