97,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','OnlyTheseUsers',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(49543,6680,6,0,1,0,'Page','2012-05-25 11:46:39','2013-10-04 14:18:32','under-the-hood','Under the hood',NULL,'<p>Behind the clean CMS and website presentation sits <a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/framework-introduction/\">Silverstripe Framework</a>. Website developers use the framework to write code to create templates, logic, and tailor how the CMS works. Developers get the power and flexibility of (object oriented PHP 5.3+) code, designers get the freedom of HTML5 and CSS, and content authors get the simplicity of a tailored CMS.</p>\n<p><img class=\"leftAlone\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/silverstripe-php-code-sample.png\" alt=\"silverstripe php code sample\" width=\"298\" height=\"162\"/></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,10,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,7198,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(49544,6680,7,0,1,0,'Page','2012-05-25 11:46:39','2013-10-04 14:18:32','under-the-hood','Under the hood',NULL,'<p>Behind the clean CMS and website presentation sits <a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/framework-introduction/\">Silverstripe Framework</a>. Website developers use the framework to write code to create templates, logic, and tailor how the CMS works. Developers get the power and flexibility of (object oriented PHP 5.3+) code, designers get the freedom of HTML5 and CSS, and content authors get the simplicity of a tailored CMS.</p>\n<p><img class=\"leftAlone\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/silverstripe-php-code-sample.png\" alt=\"silverstripe php code sample\" width=\"298\" height=\"162\"/></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,7198,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(49545,6678,6,0,1,0,'Page','2012-05-25 10:58:19','2013-10-04 14:18:49','styles','Styles',NULL,'<p>Pages of your website should be typographically consistent. Content authors can choose from a list of styles by a designer (in a CSS file). R