m a variety of sites into your page, thanks to the magic of oEmbed! Just click the \"insert media\" button (it looks like a picture of a tree) and enter the URL of your video (YouTube, Vimeo), photo (Flickr, or URL).</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/434a3c357d/media-from-web.png\" id=\"47491\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>\n<div class=\"captionImage leftAlone\" style=\"width: 600px;\">\n<p class=\"caption\"></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(49740,6672,21,1,505,505,'Page','2012-05-24 17:32:21','2025-06-24 00:17:26','media-insertion','Media insertion',NULL,'<p>You can insert media from a variety of sites into your page, thanks to the magic of oEmbed! Just click the \"insert media\" button (it looks like a picture of a tree) and enter the URL of your video (YouTube, Vimeo), photo (Flickr, or URL).</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/434a3c357d/media-from-web.png\" id=\"47491\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>\n<div class=\"captionImage leftAlone\" style=\"width: 600px;\">\n<p class=\"caption\"></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(49741,6681,13,0,505,0,'Page','2012-05-25 13:52:37','2025-06-24 00:18:06','security-and-audit-trail','Security & Audit Trail',NULL,'<p>Every save made to a page contributes to an audit trail. You can compare old versions with each other and roll back to them in the History tab.</p>\n<p>A powerful security system allows viewing and editing of pages to be restricted to various users. Users and groups can be created and this can all provide the basis for secure login areas or more elaborate publishing workflow.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/page-settings.png\" id=\"47489\" width=\"600\" height=\"475\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,9,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','OnlyTheseUsers',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(49742,6681,14,1,505,505,'Page','2012-05-25 13:52:37','2025-06-24 00:18:06','security-and-audit-trail','Security & Audit Trail',NULL,'<p>Every save made to a page contributes to an audit trail. You can compare old versions with each other and roll back to them in the History tab.</p>\n<p>A powerful security system allows viewing and editing of pages to be restricted to various users. Users and groups can be created and this can all provide the basis for secure login areas or more elaborate publishing workflow.</p>\n<p>[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/page-settings.png\" id=\"47489\" width=\"600\" height=\"475\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,9,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','OnlyTheseUsers',NULL,0,0,0,0,1),(49743,7203,33,0,505,0,'Page','2013-10-15 11:58:53','2025-06-24 00:18:24','styles-demo','Styles Demo',NULL,'<h2>Typography</h2>\n<p class=\"intro\">Editors have the power to alter the appearance of content within the site using the powerful built-in editor. For example, this introductory text which can be added with the styles that drop down within the CMS editor.</p>\n<p class=\"intro\">[image src=\"/assets/Uploads/text-style.png\" id=\"47490\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" class=\"leftAlone ss-htmleditorfield-file image\"]</p>\n<div class=\"captionImage leftAlone\" style=\"width: 600px;\">CMS editor</div>\n<p>The typography of the Simple theme is designed to create a strong hierarchy with basic styles. The primary header font is \"Cambo Regular\" which is not a regular web font but provides a good example of how custom web fonts from services like&nbsp;<a title=\"Visit typekit.com\" href=\"https://typekit.com/\">Typekit</a> and <a title=\"Visit Google Fonts\" href=\"http://ww